{
  "stem": "27390.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came home in the evenings, we had to queue up for the rations, in the co-ops, to get the rations.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- sometimes it took hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came home, knocked out, until we managed to get the ration.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must mention, around that time, in 1941, a lot of Jews were brought in, from all different countries in Europe, into the ghetto, from Germany, from Austria, from Luxembourg, from France.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thousands-- about 40,000, 50,000 Jews came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were told that they're coming to an autonomous Jewish region, and they will be offered jobs in their professions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they will be-- they will give-- be given a good living accommodation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they told us that, when they left their counties, they were put on proper passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as they came near the Polish border, they were transferred from these trains into cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they arrived in the ghetto, they were-- because they were told that this is only temporary, and they will be transferred back, again, into-- into passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they arrived in the ghetto, they realized what's happened to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- in the beginning, they-- they were taken aback.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They looked at us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were already like skeletons in rags.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they came, the women, with nice hairstyles and beautiful outfits, the men in nice overcoats, with loads of luggage, they let them bring with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the beginning, they couldn't take the food, what they were offered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we used to stand, queuing up, as they were throwing away the food they were offered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We used to pick it up, because we were starving already and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've got to go to an engagement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Will you be long?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
